With a vibrantly rich multifaceted 8 mm high quality almandite garnet, this 14k rose (pink) gold filled stackable ring is lovely and perfect for everyday wear. It absolutely sparkles and looks equally elegant worn alone, with one band or additional stacking rings. The almandite garnet has a lovely, intense wine color, and it is clean material, very sparkly.

