The garnet sits atop one of my handforged 14k rose (pink) gold filled beaded / dotted bands made with 14GA (1.5mm) wire. The bezel is also made of 14k rose gold filled metal sheet.

Here are the details:
- Garnet is the January birthstone;
- Stone size: 8mm;
- Stone shape: Round;
- Approx carats per stone: 2.5;
- Stone country of Origin: Mozambique;
- Stone treatment: None;
- Stone clarity: Almost loupe clean (VVS)


♥Please Note: This ring is made to order in your size. Please write your ring size in the "notes to seller" box at checkout. 

I stand by my jewelry as quality handmade art. If you have any problems with it - what so ever - Please do not hesitate to contact me. I want you to be happy with the piece of jewelry you have purchased from me! 

All custom sized rings take 1-2 weeks to make. I'm always willing to work with you if you are in need of something quickly - but please contact me before purchasing to make sure I can do it.
